BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:6ahAvXJx9I5a_KGId2Ofx
SUMMARY:IMPROV 100 SATURDAYS- Intro to Improv: Say Yes!\\\, SPRING'26
DTSTAMP:20260308T010216Z
DTSTART:20260321T120000Z
DESCRIPTION:Discover Unexpected Productions’ philosophy of improvisation\\\
	, developed over our 43 years of improvising in Seattle! \\nYou’ll learn h
	ow to actively listen\\\, to use your own life to create collaborative sto
	ries\\\, and you’ll work on the fundamental principles of improvisation: w
	hat it means to say\\\, “Yes\\\, And”\\\, how to tell stories that include
	 everyone in the room\\\, how to stop worrying about failing\\\, and the g
	ames and concepts behind what we do on stages around the world! \\nUnder t
	he guidance of one of our best Seattle improv teachers\\\, you will learn 
	to:· \\n\\nBe a Better Listener\\nConquer Fears\\nSpark Creativity\\nMeet 
	New People & Make New Friends\\nBecome a Better Problem Solver\\nGain Conf
	idence·\\nFail With Grace (and Maybe Even Enjoy It)\\nSay Yes More in Your
	 Life\\nGet Out of Your Comfort Zone\\nBecome a Better Public Speaker\\nDi
	scover More About Yourself\\n…and have a blast doing it!\\n\\nTime and Dat
	es: Saturdays for eight (8) weeks\\\, from March 21 to May 9\\\, 12pm to 2
	:30pm. \\nNOTE: Attendance at the first session of your course is mandator
	y as it sets the agenda for the entire quarter. If you think you will have
	 to miss the first class\\\, please consider registering for the next quar
	ter. \\nNo Prerequisites. All students begin at this level\\\, even those 
	with existing improv experience. It’s a prerequisite to the other levels. 
	\\nLocation: 650 S Orcas St\\\, Room 217\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98108 (In 
	Georgetown\\\, south of downtown\\\, with plenty of parking.) \\nMaximum S
	tudents: 16 \\nCost: Ticket price $295.00 \\nAge: 18 and above \\n**Cancel
	lation policy: If you must cancel before the first class\\\, we can only o
	ffer credit towards the same level class next quarter. We are unable to of
	fer refunds. If you cancel after the first class we cannot offer credit to
	wards a future class. Again\\\, we are unable to offer refunds.\n\nhttps:/
	/www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/improv-100-saturdays-intro-to-improv-
	say-yes-spring26/\n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/improv-100-saturdays-intro-
	to-improv-say-yes-spring26/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions Improv School ISSAQUAH/EASTSIDE\\\, 1315 NW
	 Mall Street\\\, Suite 4\\\, Issaquah\\\, WA\\\, 98108\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
